snippet.title: Bio_100% // Polestar A Course - Retrogaming Gameplay [Racing / PC-98 / No Commentary]
snippet.description:
Polestar Gameplay (Not Superplay / No Cheat / No State)
Developer : Bio_100% / Year 1995 / Platform : PC-9801 Series
Play with Retroarch 1.7.3 + Neko Project Kai 0.86

*WARNING: This is not the actual soundtrack.
Since I don't have a playback device (SC-55), music was added during the video editing process.
Original OST is here.
http://bio100.jp/game_music/archive/music04.html#top4

**Gameplay
Arrow L and R keys or Joystick : Steering
Button 1 : Accel / Button 2 : Brake

**Staff
Game Design ＆ Programming : metys
Level Design Assistant : Ascomoid
Music : fin, TODOS
Sound Effect : SuCa

**Infomation
Official Site (JP)
